('b4d6f923a1e5db83797f03b05dfff24f18e53b00', '2014-02-26', '2014-02-27', 'Legals', '\n    <P><B> THE IOWA DISTRICT COURT - POLK COUNTY </B></P><P><B> PROBATE NO. ESPRO 66280 </B></P><P><B> NOTICE OF PROBATE OF WILL, OF APPOINTMENT OF EXECUTOR, AND NOTICE </B></P><P><B> TO CREDITORS </B></P><P> IN THE MATTER OF THE</P><P>ESTATE OF LOUISE STEVENSON, DECEASED</P><P>To all persons interested in the estate of Louise Stevenson, Deceased, who died on or about the January 8, 2014:</P><P>You are hereby notified that on the 4th day of February, 2014, the last will and testament of Louise Stevenson, deceased, bearing date of the 17th day of November, 2006, was admitted to probate in the above named court and that Laura N. James and Anita K. Stevenson was appointed executor of the estate. Any action to set aside the will must be brought in the District Court of said county within the later to occur of four months from the date of the second publication of this notice or one month from the date of mailing of this notice to all heirs of the Decedent and devisees under the will whose identities are reasonably ascertainable, or thereafter be forever barred.</P><P>Notice is further given that all persons indebted to the estate are requested to make immediate payment to the undersigned, and creditors having claims against the estate shall file them with the clerk of the above named District Court, as provided by law, duly authenticated, for allowance, and unless so filed by the later to occur of four months from the second publication of this notice or one month from the date of mailing of this notice (unless otherwise allowed or paid) a claim is thereafter forever barred.</P><P>Dated this 7th day of February, 2014.</P><P>Laura N. James</P><P>Executor of Estate</P><P>201 W. 125th Place</P><P>Crown Point, IN 46307</P><P>Anita K. Stevenson</P><P>4005 Pommel Place</P><P>West Des Moines, IA 50265</P><P>Martin C. Sprock,</P><P>ICS PIN No: AT0007447</P><P>Patterson Law Firm, L.L.P.</P><P>Attorney for Executor</P><P>505 Fifth Avenue, Suite 729</P><P>Des Moines, Iowa 50309</P><P>Date of second publication:</P><P>3rd day of March, 2014</P><P>Probate Code Section 304 </P>\n  '),
